Comment: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:00.12,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:120120,120120}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:00.58,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:120587,120587}Maya's Helen Keller impressed the audience with a different style from Ayumi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:06.79,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:126793,126793}In the meantime, her missing mother was spending her days in a hospital in Nagano and Maya was being nominated for Best Supporting Actress at the Academy Awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.18,0:02:27.18,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141183,147189}{\an5\pos(766,700)\fscy95\blur1\fad(400,0)}—Episode 22—\NNew Doors
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147614,147614}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149482,149482}Where are you going, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.65,0:02:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151651,151651}Oh, Rei, I'm going back to Yokohama to see if the owner of Manpuku Ken ever found out where my mother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159192,159192}Maya, what are you talking about?\NToday is the awards day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.12,0:02:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163129,163129}She's supposed to call you when she finds out where your mother is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166900,166900}Now, get ready,\Nor you'll be made ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.70,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170704,170704}Hurry, hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:02:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177944,177944}It's almost time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:178378,178378}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.71,0:03:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181715,181715}What should I do about the purple roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.65,0:03:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185652,185652}Should I arrange\Nto send some to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189622,189622}Tonight's party will be the first big award for Ms. Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196196,196196}You must be misunderstanding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198631,198631}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199933,199933}Why should I have to send her some purple roses?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.63,0:03:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204637,204637}Because you lover her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205372,205372}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207707,207707}Or is it because of guilt?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217417,217417}You think I love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218852,218852}No way. Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.18,0:03:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221187,221187}Mr. Masumi, you are denying your own emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.96,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226960,226960}You understand her talent better than anyone, and you truly love her true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233233,233233}But, whenever you interact with her, you act very cold because of your social status.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:03:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238038,238038}To escape feeling guilty, you send her purple roses and keep on encouraging her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244911,244911}You are Mr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249949,249949}But that's just cowardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.98,0:04:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253987,253987}Why don't you throw away\Nyour mask as Mr. Purple Rose…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.35,0:04:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258358,258358}…and show affection as who you\Nreally are, Mr. Hayami Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.96,0:04:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262962,262962}Mr. Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.93,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:267934,267934}You are acting strange today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274140,274140}Please arrange the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276676,276676}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.44,0:04:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280447,280447}{\i1}…and show affection as who\Nyou really are, Mr. Hayami Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297297,297297}Here's your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.79,0:04:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:297797,297797}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308975,308975}This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.05,0:05:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318051,318051}Metropolitan Entertainment is doing great this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.78,0:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321788,321788}Look at how beautiful she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324557,324557}As soon as she steps in,\Nthe whole place becomes brighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327594,327594}She was born to be a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329896,329896}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.26,0:05:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333266,333266}{\i1}She's so confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336069,336069}{\i1}It must be some kind of mistake that I have more of a chance at winning the award than she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:340006,340006}{\i1}Yes, it's just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342609,342609}{\i1}I always wake myself just before the best part.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.98,0:05:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:348982,348982}Ladies and gentlemen, let us start the Academy Awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:58.39,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:358391,358391}The nominations for the awards and their presentations were carried out by divisions such as Music Division, Traditional Dance Division, and Western Music Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.33,0:06:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367334,367334}Now, the Stage Drama Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.07,0:06:13.07,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:373073,373073}After many awards, the\NBest Supporting Actor was announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:17.81,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:377811,377811}Then it was time for the\NBest Supporting Actress award.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.05,0:06:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385051,385051}The award for\NBest Supporting Actress…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389122,389122}…goes to Helen Keller in\N"The Miracle Worker…"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399466,399466}…Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.87,0:06:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409876,409876}Ms. Kitajima Maya, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.81,0:06:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413813,413813}Please come to the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416516,416516}M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.58,0:07:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422589,422589}{\i1}This must be a dream.\NA dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425325,425325}The Academy Award for\NBest Supporting Actress: Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:430764,430764}Your performance in "The Miracle Worker"\Nhas a freshness…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.36,0:07:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435368,435368}…that has never been seen before\Nand lends tremendous emotion to the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439673,439673}{\i1}I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.64,0:07:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442642,442642}{\i1}That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.97,0:07:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:444978,444978}{\i1}I see, I know now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.91,0:07:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449916,449916}Oh, I feel like I'm still dreaming,\Nbut ouch…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.68,0:07:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455689,455689}…it's not a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.62,0:07:39.62,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:459626,459626}Then the Best Actor and Best Actress\Nwere announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:44.13,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:464130,464130}Himekawa Utako won the Best Actress\Naward for her role as Annie Sullivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471705,471705}What an irony that her mother\Nand her rival both got awarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475742,475742}But it will make the best headline.\N"The Defeat of a Genius Actress, Himekawa Ayumi."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.65,0:08:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485652,485652}Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498865,498865}Congratulations, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501401,501401}Thank you, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505271,505271}Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506506,506506}{\i1}Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509175,509175}Congratulations, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.57,0:08:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:512579,512579}Thank you, Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.21,0:08:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515215,515215}But I still don't think\Nyou defeated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.01,0:08:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519019,519019}I finally understood\Nwhen I heard the award.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:522455,522455}I still think I played\Nthe perfect Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525725,525725}If you'd have played a perfect Helen better\Nthan I did, then I'd have really lost this award.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534167,534167}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:08:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535802,535802}{\i1}Your performance in "The Miracle Worker"\Nhas brought a freshness that has never been seen before…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.90,0:09:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:541908,541908}Your Helen was a new Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.71,0:09:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543710,543710}This means that your Helen and mine\Nwere totally different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547080,547080}I have regained my confidence that mine was truly a perfect Helen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.11,0:09:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551117,551117}Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:15.28,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:555288,555288}After the awards were given,\Nthe reception was held.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.89,0:09:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559893,559893}There is no contention in that Metropolitan Entertainment monopolized all twelve divisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565298,565298}It is no wonder why your father can leave the business up to you with no worries, Mr. Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569669,569669}I bet he would be even more at ease if you got married now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574607,574607}Are you seeing anyone right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:577277,577277}No, unfortunately, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579879,579879}Well, we hear\Nyou are a workaholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591358,591358}Would you like to dance with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:09:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594694,594694}Congratulations for your award.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.69,0:09:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596696,596696}T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:09:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:599032,599032}An award-winning star\Nshould not be a wallflower.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601835,601835}I don't know how to dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.70,0:10:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:607707,607707}That's okay.\NJust follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623223,623223}Good, you're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.95,0:10:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624958,624958}Why did you ask me to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.86,0:10:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627861,627861}You were the vanguard in promoting\NMetropolitan Entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635035,635035}Everyone's watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.93,0:10:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636936,636936}Just let them.\NIt will be good advertisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639205,639205}Advertisement?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640640,640640}You will be a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640840,640840}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.64,0:10:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643643,643643}You can't be a star if you are shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645645,645645}You have to learn how to sell yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.41,0:10:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647414,647414}You can't be successful with just your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:650316,650316}Why… why are you\Ntelling me all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.82,0:10:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654821,654821}{\i1}Why don't you, as Hayami Masumi,\Nshow your affection to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660326,660326}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:662128,662128}I don't want to break\Na golden egg before it hatches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667033,667033}I won't be a golden egg\Nfor Metropolitan Entertainment!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.83,0:11:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669836,669836}Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681214,681214}{\i1}This feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692592,692592}{\i1}That summer…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697664,697664}{\i1}…he's Mr. Purple Rose?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700834,700834}{\i1}Is he?
Comment: 0,0:11:54.75,0:11:54.75,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:714756,714756}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:11:58.50,0:11:58.50,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:718509,718509}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:01.47,0:12:01.47,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:721471,721471}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742409,742409}You are too young\Nfor the love scene, little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745178,745178}What happened? Has the heat\Nfrom the hall affected you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.11,0:12:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753119,753119}{\i1}No way.\NThat cold bastard can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.68,0:12:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755689,755689}{\i1}It's just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757157,757157}{\i1}Did she notice?\NNo, she couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:766833,766833}Hello, Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.26,0:12:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768268,768268}Did you come to see your good student's award presentation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770370,770370}A good student?\NYes, some future good students.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.84,0:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:777844,777844}Future good students?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.31,0:13:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783316,783316}Everyone, we have\Na surprise guest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786419,786419}A phenomenal actress, a lily of the stage drama world…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789856,789856}…and the actress from "The Crimson Goddess", Miss Tsukikage Chigusa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793159,793159}The teacher of Himekawa Utako,\Nwho won Best Actress award…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798031,798031}…and also of Kitajima Maya,\Nthe Best Supporting Actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808408,808408}How are you, Miss Tsukikage?\NAny words of celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812312,812312}Yes. Both Helens have some extraordinary talents.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.21,0:13:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:816216,816216}I must say they are suited to be candidates for "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821254,821254}Ms. Kitajima Maya, Ms. Himekawa Ayumi.\NPlease come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828762,828762}Ayumi, would you like to practice for "The Crimson Goddess" with Maya here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834034,834034}Miss Tsukikage…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836569,836569}Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837904,837904}I would love to.\NI would love to, Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843543,843543}Everyone, I would like to take advantage of this opportunity…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.58,0:14:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:848581,848581}…to introduce the two candidates for "The Crimson Goddess":\NKitajima Maya and Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852385,852385}The battle has just begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.72,0:14:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855722,855722}I will see how they grow\Nas actresses, and eventually…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860927,860927}…choose one of the two\Nfor "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.33,0:14:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869336,869336}Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871938,871938}Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.44,0:14:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882449,882449}You had the first move.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.58,0:14:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884584,884584}I was going to purchase\N"The Crimson Goddess…"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:889222,889222}…and give actresses nationwide\Nthe opportunity to compete.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.39,0:14:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893393,893393}To promote the name\Nof Metropolitan Entertainment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896796,896796}Can I at least still hope for\Nthe play rights, Miss Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:902769,902769}I wouldn't give up the play rights\Neven if I were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.87,0:15:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:905872,905872}No more little tricks of yours, since we have many witnesses now. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.45,0:15:19.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:919452,919452}There's a phone call for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.92,0:15:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923923,923923}Hello.\NThis is Maya speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.19,0:15:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926192,926192}Oh, Sakurakōji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927961,927961}Congratulations.\NI'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:929996,929996}You're the first 16 year-old\Nto win an Academy Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933333,933333}Thank you.\NYes, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937904,937904}…America?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.23,0:15:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939239,939239}I'm leaving tomorrow at twelve o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941574,941574}I'm going to go\Nto acting school there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.11,0:15:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944110,944110}I want to start learning\Nfrom scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.81,0:15:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:949816,949816}I'll come back\Nwith ability and confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953186,953186}I'll be there,\Nat the airport tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:955822,955822}I'll be there, Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.49,0:16:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:960493,960493}See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.12,0:16:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:963129,963129}Maya, your mother called.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965932,965932}What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967734,967734}The lady from Manpuku Ken just called the landlord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.70,0:16:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972706,972706}She heard from your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983083,983083}Hey, you keep looking at your watch.\NAre you expecting someone important?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989556,989556}No, no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.49,0:16:31.49,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:991491,991491}Manpuku Ken
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.02,0:16:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:993026,993026}About eight o'clock\Nin the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:994494,994494}She said she was fine\Nand not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.99,0:16:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996996,996996}I asked her where she was,\Nbut then she hung up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.13,0:16:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1000133,1000133}Is that so…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001868,1001868}Fukui Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003870,1003870}{\i1}Maya, I've lost my sight,\Nbut I can still see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010143,1010143}{\i1}I'm always watching you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1015548,1015548}Next time she calls, I'll be sure\Nto find out where she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.75,0:16:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1018752,1018752}So don't feel bad, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:16:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1019319,1019319}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.09,0:17:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027093,1027093}Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1032098,1032098}{\i1}Maya, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038571,1038571}A TV series?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.87,0:17:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039873,1039873}He brought the offer\Nfrom the TV station for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043977,1043977}He also has a television series for Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1048515,1048515}Masumi must be caring for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052152,1052152}To be fair to the candidates\Nof "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.79,0:17:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056790,1056790}Masumi finally feels like letting the two candidates, Maya and Ayumi, grow for "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.03,0:17:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1064030,1064030}A TV series for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068535,1068535}Maya, I don't know how well your act will carry to television, or how well you'll do in the TV world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.80,0:17:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1075809,1075809}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:17:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077911,1077911}You might become a star,\Nyou might not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1082182,1082182}You might become worthless as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086019,1086019}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1088455,1088455}Any route you take,\Nthe road will be rough and bumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091658,1091658}I… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094027,1094027}What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095729,1095729}Should I decline?\NTeacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098865,1098865}It is up to you\Nto make that decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.13,0:18:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1102135,1102135}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.57,0:18:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1106573,1106573}{\i1}You might even become worthless as an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.47,0:18:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1111478,1111478}{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116349,1116349}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.18,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122188,1122188}Okay, let her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.55,0:18:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124557,1124557}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129462,1129462}Hello, little girl.\NWelcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132165,1132165}H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133700,1133700}Don't be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.76,0:18:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135769,1135769}I see. This is the first time\Nyou've been here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.57,0:18:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138571,1138571}You can have a seat there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.77,0:19:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140774,1140774}No, thank you. I'm just here\Nto answer your proposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146246,1146246}I… I accept your offer\Nfor the TV series.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150016,1150016}Good. I thought you'd reject it,\Nsince you don't like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.99,0:19:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1156990,1156990}What made you decide?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.42,0:19:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1160427,1160427}Do you want to be know on\Ntelevision and become a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.49,0:19:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163496,1163496}This is for my mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.46,0:19:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1165465,1165465}Your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167667,1167667}If I'm on TV, my mother\Nmight see me someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.30,0:19:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1171304,1171304}Then I might be able to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173840,1173840}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1175975,1175975}Also, I'd like to thank you for this one, but I don't intend to owe Metropolitan Entertainment a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182682,1182682}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189189,1189189}She had the upper hand, Mr. Masumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.79,0:19:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191791,1191791}Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.42,0:19:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195428,1195428}Even if it's difficult, she has to keep on walking without looking back once she starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202102,1202102}She finally started walking, all by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.70,0:20:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1206706,1206706}Oh, that Mr. Purple Rose guy you mentioned before. She doesn't need him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213780,1213780}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:42.50,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1242509,1242509}Maya has moved forward to a new world,\Nfrom the stage to television.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.84,0:20:47.84,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1247847,1247847}Ayumi, who has refused all television offers in the past…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1251985,1251985}…has accepted the new challenge\Nand jumped into the new world as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.95,0:20:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1255955,1255955}{\i1}Maya, do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.05,0:20:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1258058,1258058}{\i1}Try and see how much your acting ability on stage will work for television.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.73,0:21:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266733,1266733}{\i1}Go on ahead, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.90,0:21:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268902,1268902}{\i1}Be destroyed as an actress, or overcome it and jump even further ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.64,0:21:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274641,1274641}{\i1}What's important for you\Nis how you will grow as a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.08,0:21:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1282082,1282082}{\i1}Ayumi, I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.25,0:21:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1284250,1284250}{\i1}You'll not only notice my freshness and originality, but also my ability…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.29,0:21:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290290,1290290}{\i1}…and someday…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1301468,1301468}The battle has just began.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1305205,1305205}I will see how they grow as actresses…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.90,0:21:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1309909,1309909}…and eventually choose the one of the two for "The Crimson Goddess."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.96,0:22:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329963,1329963}The roads you take might be different, but your destination is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1335502,1335502}Now, both of you, start walking towards your goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.37,0:22:23.37,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1343376,1343376}Now, new doors have been opened.
